# Agent workflow

**Issues first:** see [work-tracking.mdc](work-tracking.mdc). No feature work without a board issue unless user waives tracking for a trivial doc typo.

| Situation | Action |
|-----------|--------|
| New feature, bugfix, refactor | Create issue via `scripts/arrdash-issue-create.sh`, then implement |
| User says "just document" / typo | May skip issue if explicitly scoped |
| Ready to merge | PR with `Closes #N`, CHANGELOG + docs updated |
| Deploy | User runs `docker compose build && docker compose up -d` on Unraid |

Do not auto-commit or push unless the user asks. Do not merge PRs without user approval.
